'''CIWEC Clinic Travel Medicine Center''' , also known as CIWEC Hospital, is a specialist in travel related illnesses and has been serving nationals, travelers and the expatriate community since 1982.{{citation needed|date=November 2017}} It is the first travel medicine center situated in Asia. CIWEC is well known in the expatriate community to provide excellent medical care. [[Nepal]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ciwec-clinic.com/ |title=CIWEC Clinic |publisher=CIWEC Clinic |date= |accessdate=2013-11-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=steveranger |url=http://climbhighhimalaya.com/ciwec-clinic/ |title=Climb High use the CIWEC Clinic in Kathmandu |publisher=climb high himalaya |date=2013-06-28 |accessdate=2013-11-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202235509/http://climbhighhimalaya.com/ciwec-clinic/ |archivedate=2013-12-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tourismthamel.com/visitors_service/clinic/details/ciwec-clinic-travel-medicine-center |title=CIWEC Clinic Travel Medicine Center - Eye Clinic/Clinic Health, Kathmandu, Nepal |publisher=TourismThamel |date= |accessdate=2013-11-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Category: Links |url=http://himalayanrescue.org/ciwec-clinic-travel-medicine-center-kathmandu.html |title=ciwec-clinic-travel-medicine-center-kathmandu |publisher=Himalayanrescue.org |date= |accessdate=2013-11-26}}</ref>
